    "body": "### Problem\n\nIf `'smoothscroll'` and `'number'` is set, nvim crashes when reducing the size of a vertical split window that contains smoothscrolled text past the number column.\r\n\r\nBacktrace\r\n```\r\nProgram received signal SIGFPE, Arithmetic exception.\r\n0x00000000006663a4 in mouse_comp_pos (win=0xad82e0, rowp=0x7fffffffd7f0, colp=0x7fffffffd7f4, lnump=0x7fffffffd8dc) at /home/neovim/src/nvim/mouse.c:1629\r\n1629            skip_lines = (win->w_skipcol - width1) / (width1 + win_col_off2(win)) + 1;\r\n(gdb) bt\r\n#0  0x00000000006663a4 in mouse_comp_pos (win=0xad82e0, rowp=0x7fffffffd7f0, colp=0x7fffffffd7f4, lnump=0x7fffffffd8dc) at /home/neovim/src/nvim/mouse.c:1629\r\n#1  0x0000000000662dd2 in get_fpos_of_mouse (mpos=0x7fffffffd8dc) at /home/neovim/src/nvim/mouse.c:243\r\n#2  0x00000000006635c0 in do_mouse (oap=0x7fffffffd9f8, c=-11773, dir=-1, count=1, fixindent=false) at /home/neovim/src/nvim/mouse.c:555\r\n#3  0x0000000000666238 in nv_mouse (cap=0x7fffffffda50) at /home/neovim/src/nvim/mouse.c:1591\r\n#4  0x0000000000676430 in normal_execute (state=0x7fffffffd9e0, key=-11773) at /home/neovim/src/nvim/normal.c:1229\r\n#5  0x0000000000757daf in state_enter (s=0x7fffffffd9e0) at /home/neovim/src/nvim/state.c:101\r\n#6  0x000000000067465c in normal_enter (cmdwin=false, noexmode=false) at /home/neovim/src/nvim/normal.c:518\r\n#7  0x000000000061a505 in main (argc=7, argv=0x7fffffffddb8) at /home/neovim/src/nvim/main.c:664\r\n```\n\n### Steps to reproduce\n\nstep 1. run nvim with the following command \r\n```\r\nnvim --clean -S <(tee << 'EOF'\r\n    set smoothscroll number mouse=a\r\n    vnew\r\n    call setline(1, 'Lorem ipsum dolor sit amet, consectetur adipiscing elit, sed do eiusmod tempor incididunt ut labore et dolore magna aliqua.')\r\n    exe \"normal! \\<C-e>\"\r\nEOF\r\n)\r\n```\r\n![image](https://github.com/neovim/neovim/assets/19489738/8d96236a-7bf7-4acc-a14d-2227309e93f4)\r\n\r\nstep 2. click and drag the vertical window separator all the way to the left.\r\n![image](https://github.com/neovim/neovim/assets/19489738/9925d957-1df4-4b0e-989c-8610fcbadc0f)\r\n\r\ncrash\n\n### Expected behavior\n\nno crash\n\n### Neovim version (nvim -v)\n\n0.10 d3fa88b70f6f96ec4bc505968afec1dedb3b450b\n\n### Vim (not Nvim) behaves the same?\n\nno, 9.1.0400\n\n### Operating system/version\n\nubuntu 22.04\n\n### Terminal name/version\n\nGNOME Terminal 3.44.0 using VTE 0.68.0 +BIDI +GNUTLS +ICU +SYSTEMD\n\n### $TERM environment variable\n\ntmux-256color\n\n### Installation\n\nbuild from repo",
